{"type": "article", "id": 16545, "title": "要是像这19条说的这样，你们大约就不再相爱了吧 | 好奇心研究所", "description": "我的天空，星星都瞎了。", "date": "2015-10-24T14:58:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6049, "name": "爱情"}, {"id": 17713, "name": "友情"}], "category": 3, "column": 33, "author": 130547, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 146, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134626Pnsu8bv3MKJ9C0NX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1.  眼神。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134617HvEUPRNO3BiM45og.jpg\" width=\"639\" height=\"386\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.60406886\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>2.  失踪。留下一本日记给警察。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346187z6g40HbhDCAGtBf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"719\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong>3.  聊天记录从 </strong><strong>1000 </strong><strong>条到 </strong><strong>500 </strong><strong>条到 </strong><strong>200 </strong><strong>条到两天前。电话从 </strong><strong>2 </strong><strong>小时到半小时到 </strong><strong>10 </strong><strong>分钟到两天前。 (@ Li_Ga)</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134618Zm0TNuKrB8zcbDLh.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"601\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:start;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>4.  不停说谎。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346195DnL7PocsFKy6rje.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"266\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.532\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>5.  以前喜欢合照，现在只想自拍。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134619xlgJLIOisfWGREaK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"723\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6.  以前是置顶，现在想黑名单。</strong><strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134620xXPyzhCBa2UvOScn.jpg\" width=\"580\" height=\"348\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>7.  现在嫌弃。以前不。</b><strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134620SPDYbmHpE7GxRjKN.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8.  懒得回家。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134621vDkVSUzTLXM7bW34.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"338\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.676\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><b>9.  回家就关着门。</b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><b></b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143745v4yad6UgfHi5RQnG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"484\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.44814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>10.</b>  <b>真的不想听。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346210A7Tz41twGpelHkc.gif\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><b></b></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<b><strong><b><span></span>11.  听也听不懂。</b><img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437473HdNXskRYfj02PhF.gif\" width=\"499\" height=\"374\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.749499\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<b><strong>12.  听懂也不重要。</strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b><strong></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143750Gw93fzTPuC8nI7xW.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"294\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.588\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b>13.  已经活在两个世界。</b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134622tuMopdlwP4eXs7Yh.gif\" width=\"400\" height=\"324\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.81\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14.  和别人聊天</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>吃饭</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>看电影</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>旅游</strong><strong>/</strong><strong>睡觉，更开心。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134623fmQv01W6gHIa8Ljt.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"464\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong>15.  亲不下去。</strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134623LISEHTyMiACq0JGU.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"871\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.3609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong></strong><strong>16.  笑不出来。</strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134624wTZJQWRbop7VCYGA.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"400\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75046904\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>17.  哭也嫌累。</strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134625JSEHbC0hNUTMxPjY.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>18.  不如……</strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134625MwvzFfRPctTEoB20.jpg\" width=\"626\" height=\"400\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.63897764\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong> </strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong>19.  唉。</strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><strong><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021346269wTPBytpd4AbCWJH.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"277\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.554\" data-format=\"gif\"><strong> </strong></strong></strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong><span><strong></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}